    "reasoning": "This is an interesting topic about kirigami-inspired parachutes. Kirigami is the art of cutting and folding paper, and researchers have been studying how principles from kirigami can be applied to parachute design. Let me create a comprehensive 2000-word explainer on this topic.\n\nI should cover:\n1. What kirigami is\n2. Traditional parachute design and limitations\n3. Why researchers looked at kirigami\n4. How kirigami principles apply to parachutes\n5. Benefits of kirigami-inspired designs\n6. Research examples\n7. Potential applications\n8. Challenges and future directions\n\nLet me aim for approximately 2000 words.",
